A4.text: The 2022 Winter Olympics were held from 4 to 20 February 2022 in Beijing, China, and surrounding areas with competition in selected events beginning 2 February 2022.

A5.text: The 2010 Winter Olympics were held from February 12 to 28, 2010 in Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada, with some events held in surrounding suburbs.

A6.text: The 1994 Winter Olympics were held from 12 to 27 February 1994 in and around Lillehammer, Norway.
